"I wanna know the way"
Don't we all?

"So why do something that offends someone?" 

Literally anything you do, or say, can and most likely, will offend someone. Sadly.

"do yo kno dae wae?" is pretty popular in my school. I was walking on the bus and a younger kid said "do yo kno dae wae?" and i was like "yes i know the way" and i saw my cousin and his friends go up to the door and said 'do you kno dae wae?" but his friends weren't talking to me. Pretty much all the boys in my class know the meme.
